question.title: Error to export an android app

node.contents: I am trying to export my android application in order to publish on Google play.

astNode.text: I am trying to export my android application in order to publish on Google play.

node.contents: My project includes some library dependencies that may cause this problem, because it is perfectly working for my other apps which do not have dependencies.
